text: Faustino Javier Estrada González (born 4 August 1967) is a Mexican politician from the Ecologist Green Party of Mexico. From 2006 to 2009 he served as Deputy of the LX Legislature of the Mexican Congress representing Morelos. ==References== Category:1967 births Category:Living people Category:People from Morelos Category:Members of the Chamber of Deputies (Mexico) Category:Ecologist Green Party of Mexico politicians Category:21st-century Mexican politicians
